OL,4,CFree school meals: Poorer pupils miss
OL,5,Cout in funding change, say unions
OL,6, The number of children in England
OL,7, entitled to free school meals has risen
OL,8, significantly during the pandemic.
OL,10,FNew figures from data in January show
OL,11,F20.8% - more than one in five - now
OL,12,Fqualify, up from 17.3% in January 2020.
OL,14,FSchools will eventually get additional
OL,15,Ffunding via the pupil premium, but that
OL,16,Fwill be based on older figures from
OL,17,FOctober 2020.
OL,19,FUnions say this means schools will miss
OL,20,Fout on funding but the government says
OL,21,Fit will help with budget planning.
